[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare pre-visit intake bot decomposes into ten logical stages: channel entry, input safety screening, identity and relationship verification, visit-context loading, protocol selection, adaptive question-flow orchestration, structured data extraction with screener administration, parallel crisis and acuity flagging, output safety screening, and pre-visit packet generation. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.3 carry forward; this recipe adds three new ones (intake-protocol-as-code lifecycle, validated-screener tool library governance, pre-visit packet schema management).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY ─────────────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient receives intake invitation through one of      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    the configured channels: secure email link, SMS        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    link, in-app push notification, patient-portal         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    embed when authenticated]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Greeting and disclosure]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Identifies as a chatbot, not a clinician             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - States the bot's scope (collecting information       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for the upcoming visit; not providing medical        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      advice; not performing triage; not a substitute      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for the visit)                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acknowledges that emergencies should go to 911       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Offers an immediate path to reach the clinic         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sets expectations on length and what happens         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with the data                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate session_id                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture channel, authentication context, and the     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      deep-link parameters identifying the upcoming        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      encounter                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - On resume: load partial state                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, encounter   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    reference]                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY SCREENING ────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Same primitive as the previous chapter 11 recipes,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    with intake-specific tuning:]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis detection (preempts everything; intake        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversations frequently surface crisis signals      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      because the bot is asking about how the patient      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      is doing)                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Screener-aware: the bot's PHQ-9 item 9 expects       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      a response that may match crisis patterns; the       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      crisis pipeline knows the screener context and       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handles it appropriately                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: input passes / input blocked-with-disposition] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── IDENTITY AND RELATIONSHIP VERIFICATION ────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authenticated session path (recommended default)]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient is logged into the patient portal or app     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The session conveys an authenticated patient_id      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The bot accepts the patient_id as verified           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Unauthenticated link path with one-time token]         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The intake link includes a single-use signed token   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      that authenticates the patient for this specific     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      intake session                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The bot verifies the token, binds to the patient,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and proceeds                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Proxy-completion path]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - When the visit is for a child or for a patient       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      whose access is delegated, the authenticated user    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      is the proxy, not the patient                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The bot confirms relationship at the start ("you     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      are completing this for [patient name], correct?")   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The bot's prompts adjust accordingly ("how has       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      [patient name] been feeling?")                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Step-up authentication for sensitive items]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Some institutions require step-up for items that     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      cross sensitivity thresholds (e.g., self-disclosure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      of mental-health items in an unauthenticated         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adolescent flow)                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: verified patient_id, proxy_relationship,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    assurance_level]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── VISIT-CONTEXT LOADING ─────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: encounter_context_lookup]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Visit type, scheduled provider, scheduled date,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reason-for-visit if known, encounter location        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (in-person, telehealth)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: chart_context_lookup]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active problems, current medications, known          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      allergies, recent vital signs, recent labs,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      relevant prior visit summaries                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: prior_intake_lookup]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent intake responses for the same patient         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (so the bot can confirm rather than re-collect       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      stable history items)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: patient_demographics_lookup]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Age, preferred language, accessibility               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      accommodations on file                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: structured visit context, chart context,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    prior intake context, patient demographics]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── PROTOCOL SELECTION ────────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: protocol_selector]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Inputs: visit type, encounter context, patient       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      demographics, prior intake history                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Output: the per-visit-type protocol to load          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (e.g., "primary_care_followup_v3.2",                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      "annual_physical_adult_v4.1",                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      "specialist_consult_cardiology_v2.0",                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      "behavioral_health_intake_v3.0")                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Output: the screener bundle to administer            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (e.g., PHQ-9, GAD-7 for primary-care visits          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      meeting the institutional screening cadence)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: active protocol_version, screener_bundle]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ADAPTIVE QUESTION-FLOW ORCHESTRATION ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    335[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: question_flow_state_machine]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Maintains the protocol's state                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Returns the next question to ask based on:           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    339[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      protocol position, what has been captured,           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    340[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      what the chart already provides, what branches       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    341[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      have opened or closed                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    342[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The LLM phrases the question conversationally;       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the state machine decides which question             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    344[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    345[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation loop]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot asks a phrased question                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient answers conversationally                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Extraction tool produces structured findings         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-and-acuity pipeline runs in parallel          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State machine advances; loops to next question       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    351[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      or to a follow-up branch the patient's answer        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    352[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      opened                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    353[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Branch handling]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open: patient mentions chest pain in primary-care    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      annual; cardiac-symptoms branch opens                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Close: patient denies the symptom in question;       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the negative-finding is captured and the branch      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      closes without follow-ups                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    360[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Diverge: patient brings up an unrelated significant  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    361[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      concern; the bot acknowledges, captures the          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    362[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      concern, and weaves back to the protocol             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    363[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    364[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Resumability]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    365[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persist conversation state and protocol position     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      after each captured turn                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - On resume, the bot continues from the persisted      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      position with appropriate re-greeting                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    371[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: ongoing conversation state, captured           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    findings as they accumulate]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    374[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── STRUCTURED EXTRACTION AND SCREENERS ───────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: hpi_extraction]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Extracts onset, provocation, quality, radiation,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      severity, timing, associated symptoms, alleviating   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      factors from the patient's HPI utterances            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Validates against schema                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: ros_extraction]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Extracts review-of-systems findings (positive and    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      negative) from the relevant-system questions         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Validates against schema                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: medication_reconciliation_capture]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Captures patient-reported medication updates         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      against the chart's current list                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Produces structured deltas (added, stopped,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      dose-changed, taking-as-prescribed)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Does NOT change the chart; produces                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reconciliation events for clinical review            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: allergy_reconciliation_capture]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Same pattern as medications, applied to allergies    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: history_extraction]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Past medical history, surgical history, family       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      history, social history (smoking, alcohol,           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      substance use, occupation, living situation)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Captures patient-stated detail with appropriate      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      uncertainty markers                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: screener_administer]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For each screener in the bundle, present the         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      validated item wordings, capture responses,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      compute scores per validated rules                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    411[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHQ-9, GAD-7, AUDIT-C, PROMIS instruments,           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    412[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institution-specific screeners                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    413[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Item 9 of PHQ-9 (or equivalent self-harm items)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    414[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      is wired to the crisis-and-acuity pipeline           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tool: pro_administer (optional)]                       │
