[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CRISIS AND ACUITY FLAGGING ────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Pipeline runs in parallel with the conversation]       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Crisis detection]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Suicidal ideation, active self-harm, intent          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Domestic violence, abuse, intimate-partner           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      violence, child abuse                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active substance-use crisis                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    436[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute medical emergency descriptions                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    437[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Red-flag clinical patterns]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Constellations the institution's protocol flags      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (e.g., chest-pain-with-radiation-and-exertion in     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adult, sudden-onset-severe-headache, acute           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      neurologic deficit description, GI bleeding          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      description, suicide intent endorsement on PHQ-9     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    444[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      item 9)                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    445[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each flag has a routing target (same-day             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    446[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical-staff callback, immediate crisis            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    447[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway, urgent-care redirect)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    448[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    449[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Significant new-information events]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    450[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - New diagnosis the patient mentions                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    451[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Hospitalization the chart does not show              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    452[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - New medication from another provider                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    453[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - New allergy or adverse drug reaction                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    454[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Significant change in functional status              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    455[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    456[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Pipeline output]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    457[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis flags route immediately and modify the bot's  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    458[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation flow (offer crisis resources, ask       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    459[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent for a same-day reach-out, ensure the         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    460[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient knows how to reach 911 or 988)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    461[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acuity flags route to clinical staff with the        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    462[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      relevant context attached                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - New-information events surface in the pre-visit      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      packet for the clinician's attention                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    465[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: real-time flag events plus structured          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    flag list for the pre-visit packet]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
