[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── OUTPUT SAFETY SCREENING ───────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Same primitive as the other chapter 11 recipes,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    with intake-specific checks:]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter on generated response (no diagnostic    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      speculation, no treatment recommendation, no         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      symptom interpretation, no severity assessment)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Hallucination check: did the bot reference a         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      chart fact that the chart-context tools did not      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      return? Did the bot mention a medication or          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      allergy not on the patient's list?                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persona-and-tone check: gentle, non-judgmental,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    485[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      especially around sensitive disclosures              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
