[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - New-information events                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - The conversation transcript                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - Active protocol version and screener-bundle        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        version stamps                                     │
